1.name: valencia tv cabinet
1.description: Want to make a very stylish impact in your home whilst on a budget? VALENCIA is the perfect choice. With a frame made of solid tropical wood and marble look laminate embossed on MDF top. The gorgeous two-tone patterning gives it a fabulous shine and it's also very easy to keep clean.
1.descrAdditionalInfo: An ideal TV cabinet can easily and aesthetically update the interior style of your home. A beautiful , functional and innovative entertainment unit, should personify your style.
